transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Mr. Aviles? Yeah. You advised the pharmacy to put a pause on your prescription, okay?

Speaker 2: They're going to pause it for half a year so you have time to reorder your prescription. It will still be available, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, all right. Thank you.

Speaker 2: You're welcome. You have a good one. Bye bye.
